description: Retrieves runtime information about a detector model analysis.

parameters.name: analysisId
parameters.description: The ID of the analysis result that you want to retrieve.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the analysis activity. The status can be one of the following values:
RUNNING - AWS IoT Events is analyzing your detector model. This process can take several minutes to complete.
COMPLETE - AWS IoT Events finished analyzing your detector model.
FAILED - AWS IoT Events couldn't analyze your detector model. Try again later.
